Achievements.Name: Highlight Player
Achievements.Description: Catch the ball 12 times with a diving or jumping catch.

Achievements.Name: I Got It, I Got It!
All-Star Defense
Achievements.Description: Fielders get 100 outs not including strikeouts.

Achievements.Name: Walk Off Winner
Achievements.Description: Win 5 walk-off games in your final at bat.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Control
Achievements.Description: Achieve the high score in Pitching Darts with a Challenge rule.

Achievements.Name: Pro Bowler
Achievements.Description: Achieve the high score in Pitching Bowling in a 10 frame game.

Achievements.Name: Dugout Dunker Pro
Achievements.Description: Achieve the high score in Dunk Dugout with 5 turns.

Achievements.Name: King Of Home Runs
Achievements.Description: Achieve the high score in Home Run Tourney with 20 balls.

Achievements.Name: Bat Control

Achievements.Name: Around The Horn Memory Control
Achievements.Description: Achieve the high score in Around the Horn using the 2 miss rule.

Achievements.Description: Hit a single, double, triple, and a home run as a team in a tournament game.

Achievements.Name: Triple Crown
Achievements.Description: Lead the league in batting average, home runs, and RBI's.

Achievements.Name: Shut Out
Achievements.Description: Win a game by shutout in a tournament.

Achievements.Name: No Hitter
Achievements.Description: Win a tournament game with a no hitter.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Game
Achievements.Description: Win a tournament game with no hits, walks, or errors.

Achievements.Name: Dr. K
Achievements.Description: Record 70 strikeouts in a tournament series.

Achievements.Name: Everyone Hits!
Achievements.Description: All the team members achieve base hits in the same game in a tournament.

Achievements.Name: All-Around Team Hitters
Achievements.Description: Achieve 190 base hits in a tournament series.

Achievements.Name: Scoring Frenzy
Achievements.Description: Achieve 170 runs in a tournament series.

Achievements.Name: ERA Leader
